[27/08/2018 13:50:42] <font color="#ffffff">¡Anda, Angelillo!</font>
[27/08/2018 13:50:46] <font color="#ffffff">-All right?</font>
[27/08/2018 13:50:46] <font color="#ffffff">All right, tú, andaluz honrado.</font>
